variables.name: Intro
variables.value: Ah, class has started. Welcome to Eukaryotic Molecular Biology.

variables.name: QuizIntro
variables.value: Question. Who was more responsible for the discovery of the structure of DNA, Rosalind Franklin or James Watson?

variables.name: QuizDone
variables.value: Ja, Franklin would never have elucidated base pairing from her data.

variables.name: Kinetic
variables.value: These yeast need an input of free energy to perform kinetic proofreading, and-aha-you are a source of ATP!

variables.name: Law
variables.value: Aha - your existence is violating the second law of thermodynamics. You must find a work reservoir.

variables.name: Victory
variables.value: Well done. I hope you better understand the process of science.
